 "SEC-002": {
  "status": "Fixed",
  "date": "2026-06-29",
  "commit": "296a023e",
  "note": "Code: replaced hardcoded git.token in application.properties.template with jasypt encrypted placeholder (sourced from secret store); Dockerfile already free of git-credential echo. DevOps backlog: rotate kc PAT (shihui account already suspended), purge git history (secret still in commit 8a687a99), inject git auth from Secrets Manager."
